                    Finite Element Discretization Library
                                   __
                       _ __ ___   / _|  ___  _ __ ___
                      | '_ ` _ \ | |_  / _ \| '_ ` _ \
                      | | | | | ||  _||  __/| | | | | |
                      |_| |_| |_||_|   \___||_| |_| |_|

                               https://mfem.org

This directory contains modifications of the example codes that illustrate the
use of the framework for mixed system (Par)DarcyForm and the related classes for
algebraic reduction of the system DarcyReduction or hybridization
DarcyHybridization. Operation with adaptive mesh refinement driven by
HDGErrorEstimator is also demonstrated.
